---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { getMarket } from '../lib/market.ts';
const market = getMarket(Astro.url.hostname);
const brandName = market.brandName || 'TrainedBy';
const domain = market.domain;
const effectiveDate = 'January 1, 2025';
---

<Base
  title={`Terms of Service — ${brandName}`}
  description={`Terms of Service for ${brandName}. Read our terms and conditions before using the platform.`}
>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  :root {
    --brand: #FF5C00;
    --bg: #fafaf8;
    --text: #1a1411;
    --text-2: rgba(26,20,17,0.55);
    --border: rgba(26,20,17,0.1);
    --max: 760px;
  }
  body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: 'Manrope', system-ui, sans-serif; line-height: 1.7; }
  .wrap { max-width: var(--max); margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 24px 120px; }
  .back { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; color: var(--brand); text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  h1 { font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 40px); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .meta { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-2); margin-bottom: 48px; }
  h2 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 40px 0 12px; }
  p { margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 15px; color: var(--text); }
  ul { margin: 12px 0 16px 20px; }
  li { font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  a { color: var(--brand); }
  .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 48px 0; }
  nav { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 32px 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; max-width: var(--max); margin: 0 auto; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .nav-logo { font-family: 'Manrope', system-ui, sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 18px; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 20px; }
  .nav-links a { color: var(--text-2); text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
</style>

<div class="wrap">
  <a href="/landing" class="back">← {brandName}</a>

  <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
  <p class="meta">Effective date: {effectiveDate} · Last updated: {effectiveDate}</p>

  <p>Please read these Terms of Service ("Terms") carefully before using {brandName} at {domain} (the "Service") operated by {brandName} ("we", "us", or "our"). By accessing or using the Service, you agree to be bound by these Terms.</p>

  <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
  <p>By accessing and using this Service, you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms and our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>. If you do not agree to these Terms, please do not use the Service.</p>

  <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
  <p>{brandName} is a marketplace that connects personal trainers with potential clients. We provide:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>A directory of verified personal trainers</li>
    <li>Profile pages for trainers to showcase their services</li>
    <li>Tools for trainers to manage their business and client communications</li>
    <li>Discovery tools for clients to find trainers matching their needs</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Trainer Accounts</h2>
  <p>If you register as a trainer, you agree to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Provide accurate, current, and complete information about yourself and your qualifications</li>
    <li>Maintain and promptly update your profile information</li>
    <li>Keep your account credentials confidential</li>
    <li>Be solely responsible for all activity occurring under your account</li>
    <li>Hold valid professional certifications as required by your local regulatory body</li>
    <li>Comply with all applicable laws and regulations in providing training services</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We reserve the right to verify your professional certifications and to remove any profile that contains inaccurate or misleading information.</p>

  <h2>4. Prohibited Conduct</h2>
  <p>You agree not to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Use the Service for any unlawful purpose or in violation of any applicable laws</li>
    <li>Post false, inaccurate, misleading, or defamatory content</li>
    <li>Impersonate any person or entity or falsely state your affiliation</li>
    <li>Collect or store personal data about other users without their consent</li>
    <li>Interfere with or disrupt the integrity or performance of the Service</li>
    <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to the Service or its related systems</li>
    <li>Use automated means to scrape, crawl, or data-mine the Service</li>
    <li>Transmit any viruses, malware, or other harmful code</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Content and Intellectual Property</h2>
  <p>You retain ownership of content you submit to the Service (your profile, photos, bio). By submitting content, you grant {brandName} a worldwide, non-exclusive, royalty-free license to use, reproduce, display, and distribute that content in connection with operating the Service.</p>
  <p>The {brandName} name, logo, and all related names, logos, product and service names, designs, and slogans are trademarks of {brandName}. You may not use them without our prior written permission.</p>

  <h2>6. Payments and Subscriptions</h2>
  <p>Some features of the Service require payment. All payments are processed securely through Stripe. By subscribing to a paid plan, you agree to pay the applicable fees. Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled before the renewal date.</p>
  <p>We reserve the right to change our pricing with 30 days' notice. If you do not agree with a price change, you may cancel your subscription before it takes effect.</p>
  <p>Refunds are provided at our discretion. If you believe you were charged in error, contact us within 30 days at <a href="mailto:billing@{domain}">billing@{domain}</a>.</p>

  <h2>7. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
  <p>THE SERVICE IS PROVIDED "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EITHER EXPRESS OR IMPLIED. TO THE FULLEST EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, WE DISCLAIM ALL WARRANTIES, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO IMPLIED WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, AND NON-INFRINGEMENT.</p>
  <p>We do not warrant that trainers listed on the Service hold the qualifications they claim. While we make reasonable efforts to verify certifications, users engage trainers at their own risk.</p>

  <h2>8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
  <p>TO THE FULLEST EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, {brandName} SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, INCLUDING LOSS OF PROFITS, DATA, USE, GOODWILL, OR OTHER INTANGIBLE LOSSES, ARISING OUT OF OR IN CONNECTION WITH YOUR USE OF THE SERVICE.</p>
  <p>Our total liability for any claims arising from these Terms or the Service shall not exceed the greater of (a) the amount you paid us in the 12 months preceding the claim or (b) USD $100.</p>

  <h2>9. Indemnification</h2>
  <p>You agree to indemnify and hold harmless {brandName} and its officers, directors, employees, and agents from any claims, liabilities, damages, losses, and expenses (including legal fees) arising out of or relating to your use of the Service, your violation of these Terms, or your violation of any rights of another.</p>

  <h2>10. Governing Law</h2>
  <p>These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws applicable to {brandName}'s registered place of business, without regard to conflict of law provisions. Any disputes shall be resolved through binding arbitration or in the courts of that jurisdiction.</p>

  <h2>11. Changes to Terms</h2>
  <p>We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. We will notify you of material changes by updating the "last updated" date and, where appropriate, by email. Your continued use of the Service after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.</p>

  <h2>12. Termination</h2>
  <p>We reserve the right to terminate or suspend your account and access to the Service at our sole discretion, without notice, for conduct that we believe violates these Terms or is harmful to other users, us, or third parties.</p>

  <h2>13. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at:</p>
  <p>
    <strong>{brandName}</strong><br />
    Email: <a href="mailto:legal@{domain}">legal@{domain}</a><br />
    Website: <a href="https://{domain}">https://{domain}</a>
  </p>
</div>

<nav>
  <a href="/landing" class="nav-logo">{brandName}</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
    <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
    <a href="/cookie-policy">Cookies</a>
  </div>
</nav>
</Base>
